         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">28/7/85 ¶  ¶ Could you, dear Mr Moeller, communicate with Viconde de Montserrat ¶  and Mr Carmichael ¶  in Cintra ¶  to get a publisher for your translation of the  ¶ Select plants ¶ In M to A. Möller...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">85.07.28</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Adolpho Möller</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Biblioteca do Departamento de Botânica, Universidade de Coimbra, Coimbra, Portugal.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">28/7/85</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Könnten Sie sich, lieber Herr Moeller, mit dem Viconde de Montserrat u Mr Carmichael in Cintra in Verbindung setzen, um durch deren Hülfe einen Verleger für Ihre Übersetzung der Select plants für Portugal u Brasilien zu erlangen?</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Freundschaftlich Ihr</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">28/7/85</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               </seg>Could you, dear Mr Moeller, communicate with Viconde de Montserrat<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir Francis Cook, 1st Visconde de Monserrate.</p>
               </note> and Mr Carmichael<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Not identified.</p>
               </note> in Cintra<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Alternative spelling of Sintra, Portugal.</p>
               </note> to get a publisher for your translation of the <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Select plants</seg>
               <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                     <p rend="Footnote"
                        style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In M to A. Möller, 12 July 1883, M suggested to Möller that he make a translation of M's <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Select plants</seg> and set him a copy of the then most recent English edition, B81.01.04. Möller evidently reported that no publisher could be found, and M suggested that a subsidy be sought from one of the affluent wine merchants; see M to A. Möller, 21 March 1883 (in this edition as 84-03-21c). He also suggested that Möller make enquiries about the possibility of publishing the work in Brazil (M to A. Möller, 18 May1885). <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>No translation of M's book by Möller was published; however, a Portuguese translation by Julio Henriques was published in 1905 (B05.13.01).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg> for Portugal and Brazil with their help?</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Amicably your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
         </div>
      </body>
